reviews.review_text: I was @ that show. Great to hear that show for the 1st time since I was there back in the Fall '93, the only time I ever went to the "Gahden."  Jack Straw was a great opener....Jerry broke a string during Althea or one of the 1st 3 tunes....Iko Iko shook the balcony tv monitors....Rain encore described the day's weather.  What an amazing experience.
